  "body": {
    "export_view": {
      "value": "<p>1.17.15 is a minor update including some small features and bug fixes.</p><p>Scheduled 11:30 CT on December 7, 2020</p><h3 id=\"id-1.17.15-NewCustomerSearchAlgorithm\">New Customer Search Algorithm</h3><ul><li><p>We added a new customer search algorithm that is much faster at returning matching results. The new algorithm should also rank more relevant matches higher in the list of results - one exception being if you have a custom sort applied on the customer list view.</p></li><li><p>You can try out the new algorithm by turning off the &quot;legacy customer search&quot; in your Miscellaneous Company Settings. When enabled, the new algorithm will\u00a0affect the customer list view (and global customer search) as well as the Ticket customer search.</p></li></ul><h3 id=\"id-1.17.15-InventoryPerformanceImprovements\">Inventory Performance Improvements</h3><ul><li><p>We added a number of minor performance improvements to the inventory list views. You do not need to do anything to enable this.</p></li></ul><h3 id=\"id-1.17.15-Bugfixes\">Bug fixes</h3><ul><li><p>We fixed issue where the ticket tax rate override was not overriding all applicable tax rates.</p></li><li><p>We restored the original\u00a0catalog item template download to make it easier to create imports for new items</p></li></ul>",
      "representation": "export_view",
